{
  "stem": "24163.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to be-- see, they were behind barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I explained to them in German that we would slowly but surely release them, and they would enter a hospital, which we had established on, on, at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I explained to them why they-- we, they couldn't just open the gate and let them out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were so anxious to-- naturally, they would be, since they had been imprisoned probably for many years, most of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I recall it somewhat, but probably some were from the furnace, you know, which by that time, they, of course, were had been extinct.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was numb when I was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll be very honest with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not-- I was somewhat in a state of shock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I entered the camp, the moment we came in with the Jeep, and we-- we saw the freight cars at first.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were outside on the, on the railway line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I saw all these dead people laying there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I looked into the freight cars, and they were piled up on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a bucket in the middle, which they used for a latrine, and these dead people all around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hey, this is what-- 49, 50 years or something later, and it's still-- I still see it in front of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a very shocking experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Very shocking.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was just-- I was even hoping there would still be some, some guards that we could kill.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
